{
    "title": "Open Prompt Manager — Cloud Cost & FinOps",
    "description": "AWS cost visibility for OPM — daily/monthly spend, per-service breakdown, ECS Fargate efficiency, NAT Gateway cost watch, and budget monitor status. Account 060367163877 · ap-southeast-2.",
    "tags": ["team:opm"],
    "layout_type": "ordered",
    "reflow_type": "auto",
    "notify_list": [],

    "template_variables": [
        {
            "name": "account",
            "prefix": "aws_account",
            "available_values": ["060367163877"],
            "default": "060367163877"
        }
    ],

    "widgets": [

        {
            "definition": {
                "title": "Cost at a Glance",
                "background_color": "custom_blue",
                "type": "group",
                "layout_type": "ordered",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "definition": {
                            "type": "note",
                            "content": "## AWS Account `060367163877` · ap-southeast-2\nBilling metrics update **hourly** via CloudWatch integration. Values show **month-to-date** estimated charges. Daily spend = delta between hourly readings.\n\n⚠️ **No OPM-specific cost tag yet** — ECS, EC2, and ECR line items cover the whole account. Use the ECS Fargate efficiency section to proxy OPM's share.",
                            "background_color": "yellow",
                            "font_size": "12",
                            "text_align": "left",
                            "show_tick": false,
                            "has_padding": true
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "definition": {
                            "title": "Total estimated charges — month to date (USD)",
                            "title_size": "16",
                            "title_align": "left",
                            "time": { "live_span": "1mo" },
                            "type": "query_value",
                            "requests": [
                                {
                                    "formulas": [{ "formula": "q" }],
                                    "queries": [
                                        {
                                            "data_source": "metrics",
                                            "name": "q",
                                            "query": "max:aws.billing.estimated_charges{aws_account:060367163877}"
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "conditional_formats": [
                                        { "hide_value": false, "comparator": "<",  "palette": "white_on_green",  "value": 400 },
                                        { "hide_value": false, "comparator": ">=", "palette": "white_on_yellow", "value": 400 },
                                        { "hide_value": false, "comparator": ">=", "palette": "white_on_red",    "value": 600 }
                                    ],
                                    "response_format": "scalar"
                                }
                            ],
                            "autoscale": false,
                            "custom_unit": "USD",
                            "precision": 2
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "definition": {
                            "title": "ECS estimated charges — MTD (USD)",
                            "title_size": "16",
                            "title_align": "left",
