        {
            "definition": {
                "title": "ECS Fargate — Cost Efficiency",
                "background_color": "custom_purple",
                "type": "group",
                "layout_type": "ordered",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "definition": {
                            "type": "note",
                            "content": "### Fargate Cost Proxy\nOPM runs **2 Fargate tasks** (backend + frontend). Fargate bills per vCPU-hour and GB-hour. Low CPU/memory utilisation = over-provisioned task definitions = wasted spend.\n\n**Rule of thumb:** if avg utilisation < 30% sustained, right-size the task definition.",
                            "background_color": "white",
                            "font_size": "12",
                            "text_align": "left",
                            "show_tick": false,
                            "has_padding": true
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "definition": {
                            "title": "ECS CPU utilization by service — 7 d",
                            "title_size": "13",
                            "title_align": "left",
                            "show_legend": true,
                            "legend_layout": "auto",
