        {
            "definition": {
                "title": "NAT Gateway — Network Cost Watch",
                "background_color": "custom_orange",
                "type": "group",
                "layout_type": "ordered",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "definition": {
                            "type": "note",
                            "content": "### ⚠️ Known Cost Risk: NAT Gateway\nOn **2026-04-15**, VPC endpoints were not applied — all ECR/ECS/SQS/STS traffic transited **3 NAT Gateways** at $0.059/GB, costing **$180.22 over 5 days**.\n\n**Fix applied:** 8 VPC endpoints created. Monitor alert threshold: >500 MB/hr bytes-out.\n\nIf this chart spikes, check VPC endpoint health: `aws ec2 describe-vpc-endpoints --filters Name=state,Values=available`",
                            "background_color": "white",
                            "font_size": "12",
                            "text_align": "left",
                            "show_tick": false,
                            "has_padding": true
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "definition": {
                            "title": "NAT Gateway bytes out — 7 d",
                            "title_size": "13",
                            "title_align": "left",
                            "show_legend": true,
                            "legend_layout": "auto",
                            "time": { "live_span": "1w" },
                            "type": "timeseries",
                            "requests": [
                                {
                                    "response_format": "timeseries",
                                    "queries": [
                                        {
                                            "data_source": "metrics",
                                            "name": "q",
                                            "query": "sum:aws.natgateway.bytes_out_to_destination{region:ap-southeast-2}"
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "style": { "palette": "warm" },
                                    "display_type": "line"
                                }
                            ],
                            "markers": [
                                { "value": "y = 524288000", "display_type": "error dashed", "label": "alert 500 MB/hr" }
                            ],
